data.meta_description: The funeral of William N. Williams, 61, 720 Princess Anne Road, who died Sunday, December 11, at his residence, was held from Hale's Chapel, on Tuesday. Mr. Williams was a native of North Carolina, but had spent the past 25 years here. A daughter, Mrs. Alberta Phelps survives him. Norfolk Journal and Guide, Saturday,...
